&lt;p&gt;General Manager for Obstetrics, Gynaecology and Acute Paediatrics&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen in the Women’s &amp; Children’s Division, we are looking for an exceptional and suitably experienced individual for the role of General Manager for obstetrics, gynaecology and acute paediatrics.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a highly motivated individual with excellent interpersonal skills and extensive experience in operational management to support the delivery of high-quality and efficient patient services to our families. The successful candidate will also have experience in managing key access targets (cancer and RTT) as well as experience in financial planning and staff management.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Interviews will be held in the week commencing: 30th November 2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;South Warwickshire NHS Foundation Trust promotes flexible working options on all appropriate positions and our managers welcome these discussions during the recruitment process.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameDilly WilkinsonJob titleAssociate Director of OperationsEmail addressdilly.wilkinson@swft.nhs.ukTelephone number07584 521793&lt;/p&gt;
